    <title>Error</title>
    <link href="https://kevinchengchn.github.io/2021/05/26/Error/"/>
    <id>https://kevinchengchn.github.io/2021/05/26/Error/</id>
    <published>2021-05-26T15:39:39.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-26T15:39:39.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Antd"><a href="#Antd" class="headerlink" title="Antd"></a>Antd</h3><h4 id="Modal"><a href="#Modal" class="headerlink" title="Modal"></a>Modal</h4><p><strong>解决Ant Design Modal内嵌Form表单initialValue值不动态更新问题</strong></p><blockquote><p><strong>问题分析：</strong>当我们第一次点开Modal的时候， FormItem会得到一个initialValue,但是这个值只在组件挂载的时候执行了一次， 当我们再次打开Modal窗口的时候并不会更新</p></blockquote><p><strong>解决方法：</strong></p><p>Modal窗口我们都有应用一个Visible来控制是否显示， 我们只要利用这个值得变化就可以实现Modal组件的重新挂载了</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123; Visible &amp;&amp; <span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Modal</span> <span class="attr">......</span>/&gt;</span></span> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Prettier"><a href="#Prettier" class="headerlink" title="Prettier"></a>Prettier</h3><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* prettier-ignore-start */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 忽略里面的内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* prettier-ignore-end */</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* prettier-ignore-next-line */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 忽略后面的行</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// prettier-ignore-line</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 忽略推荐所在的行</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">格式同：gitignore</span><br><span class="line">https:<span class="comment">//git-scm.com/docs/gitignore#_pattern_format</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="D:\Code\Butterfly_Cheng\source\_posts\Error.assets\image-20210820135413013.png" alt="image-20210820135413013"></p><h3 id="CI-CD"><a href="#CI-CD" class="headerlink" title="CI/CD"></a>CI/CD</h3><h4 id="Exit-Code-137"><a href="#Exit-Code-137" class="headerlink" title="Exit Code 137"></a>Exit Code 137</h4><p><strong>Ineffective mark-compacts near heap limit Allocation failed - JavaScript heap out of memory</strong></p><blockquote><p><strong>问题分析：</strong>分配失败- JavaScript堆内存不足</p></blockquote><p><strong>解决方法：</strong></p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cross-env NODE_OPTIONS=--max_old_space_size=<span class="number">4096</span> umi build</span><br><span class="line">--max-old-space-size=<span class="number">6144</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">依赖改为cdn引入</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
